# Skill Evolution Workflow

## When to Create a New Skill
- A recurring task appears at least twice.
- A workflow has strict steps and quality gates.
- A provider integration is likely to be replaced in the future.
- A repeated roadmap slice pattern needs stable prompts for weaker models.

## Skill Content Requirements
- Keep SKILL.md concise and practical.
- Document trigger conditions clearly ("use when...").
- Include project constraints:
  - React frontend
  - Flask backend
  - SQLite database
  - free APIs and free-tier AI tools
- Include test and commit gate reminders when relevant.
- Include exact input/output contracts when the skill is used with weaker models.
- Prefer checklist format with small verifiable steps.

## Typical New Skills for This Project
- Add/replace AI insight provider.
- Add/replace meme provider.
- Add/replace crypto news provider.
- Add/replace coin price provider.
- Generate Composer contract-first UI prompts for dashboard/auth/onboarding pages.
- Implement one roadmap slice end-to-end with explicit acceptance criteria.
